    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty to believe it! I have absolutely pampered this car from day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's in truly pristine condition, inside and out\u2014not a speck out of place. I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
