    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector's dream, maintained in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like shine, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seating shows no signs of bolster wear, and the interior still retains its original new-car scent. Every electronic feature and mechanical component operates with precision, backed by a meticulous, full-service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Always garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this car offers a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. It is, quite simply, the finest example of this model currently available on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
