      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is in absolutely stunning shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives just as smooth as it looks. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel without the 'brand new' price tag, this is definitely the one for you! I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so don't be a stranger\u2014let's get you behind the wheel!",
