    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a definitive example of the 996.2 generation, featuring the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus. Mechanically impeccable, the IMS bearing has been proactively retrofitted with a dual-row ceramic solution, and the rear main seal is bone dry. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, sending power to all four wheels via the viscous-coupling AWD system. It retains the widebody architecture and Turbo-spec suspension and braking systems, including four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors. The factory finish is flawless, with zero evidence of bore scoring or AOS issues. A true turnkey, investment-grade machine.",
